content_vision: Me and my friends are drinking beer. Our company is classy, and not too trashy. We seem unfriendly, but we are friendly. I'm looking for a girl to take home with me.
structure_suggestion_description: Me and my friends are drinking beer. Our company is classy, and not too trashy. We seem unfriendly, but we are friendly. I'm looking for a girl to take home with me.
text:
Intro:
her love fills my heart, like a bosons pipe,
one ninety on the speed dial, the love is hype.

Verse 1:
she's sipping on that v, feeling the effects, passion flows and the vibe connects,
she got a serious effect on me, can't resist, gotta let it be,
heavy d in the background, setting the mood, we'll let it all loose.
we don't stop at no red light, we out here wildin',
but we know one thing for sure, crack kills all smilin'.
you take my breath away with your beauty queen twirls,
oh i could feel your head up, girl, no words.
we gotta be gods in this game,

Pre-Chorus 1:
can't nobody tell us how to love,
hmphm, we'll make it work in more ways than one.

Chorus 1:
all that shit you talkin' is irrelevant
tonight we'll just drink whiskey and forget it.
she's a mastermind, she negotiates my hide,
but she only wants to kiss me, she's a pinball wizard in disguise.

Verse 2:
i won't try to raise up, just gonna keep my head down low,
when i see you ballet dancing, can't let myself be weakened and controlled.
i been working my way up, comin up like high tide,
it ain't always been good for me but i keep grindin, searching for the light at the end of my own personal tunnel, i can see it, it's getting closer, i'm almost done.
they tryna cut me loose, but i'll never break,
my homies is my family, we'll always take.
joy comes in the morning, it's good for me,
everything's clearer in the light of day, you see.

Pre-Chorus 2:
listening to jodeci, got me in my feelings,
trap cellphone ringing, can't escape these dealings,

Chorus 2:
and thumbs, keep scrolling till you hit the end,
had to stay afloat, can't let them see us bend,
had to hold on, we'll never break, we'll always transcend.
can't contain my insatiable habits, it's like an addiction,

Chorus 3:
bao, i'm the king of the block, never gonna stop,
my shit darker, this flow is my trademark.
you ready? say you ready and dat,
we'll show you how to roll with our crew, where it's at.

Bridge:
now i'm touring the world, overseas variety,
coming up like high tide, no more anxiety,
you thought i was after your body, but it's just not for me.
i'm bouncing back, better than ever before,

Outro:
up here in space, no worries or fear,
and you beg, but the end is near,

uses prechoruses to lead into the main choruses and add dynamics to the song
includes two bridges for added variation and interest
builds up to a final, powerful chorus in the outro with a new verse added for added interest and variation.
